lly oversaw proceedings, with the likes ofCeline DionandLady Gagaperforming after hundreds of athletes were paraded on boats along the river.\", \"from\": 265, \"to\": 433, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 283, \"end\": 289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"score\": 0.9994610490179721, \"rank\": 0.0005068130550161916, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the likes\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 331}, {\"ngram\": \"ofCeline\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 340}, {\"ngram\": \"hundreds\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 382}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 386, \"to\": 394}, {\"ngram\": \"boats\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 416}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 432}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fans werenot particularly overawed by the scenes in the French capital, with some claiming the opening ceremonypaled in comparison to the one that proceeded London 2012.\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 604, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 491, \"end\": 497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9928825507489385, \"rank\": 0.004014906477632703, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 592, \"end\": 603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999749954899, \"rank\": 2.4941617822751662e-08, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fans\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 439}, {\"ngram\": \"the scenes\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 483}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening\", \"from\": 526, \"to\": 537}, {\"ngram\": \"comparison\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 565}, {\"ngram\": \"the one\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 576}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some aspects of the ceremony have also came in for intense criticism, particularly a scene which saw an apparent portrayal ofLeonardo da Vinci's Last Supperpainting featuring a diverse line-up including several drag artists among those dining at the iconic table.\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 869, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some aspects\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 618}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 634}, {\"ngram\": \"intense criticism\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 674}, {\"ngram\": \"particularly a scene\", \"from\": 676, \"to\": 696}, {\"ngram\": \"an apparent portrayal\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 728}, {\"ngram\": \"da Vinci's Last Supperpainting\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 770}, {\"ngram\": \"a diverse line-up\", \"from\": 781, \"to\": 798}, {\"ngram\": \"several drag artists\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 829}, {\"ngram\": \"those dining\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 848}, {\"ngram\": \"the iconic table\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 868}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Elon Musk posted on X that the scene was'extremely disrespectful to Christians', while several religious figures condemned the depiction.\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 1008, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 871, \"end\": 880, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elon Musk\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"X\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 892}, {\"ngram\": \"the scene\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 907}, {\"ngram\": \"Christians\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 949}, {\"ngram\": \"several religious figures\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 983}, {\"ngram\": \"the depiction\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1007}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Among them was the Catholic church in France, with the Conference of French bishops saying in a statement: 'This ceremony has unfortunately included scenes of derision and mockery of Christianity, which we very deeply deplore.'\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1237, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1029, \"end\": 1037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999994159979337, \"rank\": 3.9310128602479165e-07, \"text\": \"Catholic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}, {\"begin\": 1048, \"end\": 1054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9027791222217041, \"rank\": 0.10327505882524117, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1079, \"end\": 1085, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9928825507489385, \"rank\": 0.004014906477632703, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1193, \"end\": 1205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9466647183936499, \"rank\": 0.056337528773967395, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Conference\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1075}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1115}, {\"ngram\": \"This ceremony\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1131}, {\"ngram\": \"scenes\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1165}, {\"ngram\": \"derision\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1177}, {\"ngram\": \"mockery\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1189}]}, {\"sentence\": \"US Catholic Bishop Robert Barron described the portrayal as 'gross mockery' of The Last Supper, adding: 'I love the Olympics, so I turn on the opening ceremony of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1415, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1239, \"end\": 1241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9984377012272465, \"rank\": 0.0010194927179972637, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1242, \"end\": 1250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999994159979337, \"rank\": 3.9310128602479165e-07, \"text\": \"Catholic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}, {\"begin\": 1258, \"end\": 1271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Barron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.597150412708541e-22, \"text\": \"Robert Barron\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Barron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Barron\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the portrayal\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1295}, {\"ngram\": \"gross mockery\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1313}, {\"ngram\": \"The Last Supper\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1333}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1363}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1398}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1414}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'And what do I see now?\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1440, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's in Paris, France, a city I love, I spent three years as a doctoral student there.\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1527, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1449, \"end\": 1454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999997314251138, \"rank\": 2.685750190594571e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1456, \"end\": 1462, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9027791222217041, \"rank\": 0.10327505882524117, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a city\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1470}, {\"ngram\": \"three years\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1498}, {\"ngram\": \"a doctoral student\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1520}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I see this gross mockery of the last supper and I will not describe it any further.\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1613, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this gross mockery\", \"from\": 1536, \"to\": 1554}, {\"ngram\": \"the last supper\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1573}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'France felt evidently as it's trying to put its best cultural foot forward, that the right thing to do is to mock this very central moment in Christianity where Jesus at his last supper gives his body and blood in anticipation of the cross.'\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1857, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1616, \"end\": 1622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9027791222217041, \"rank\": 0.10327505882524117, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1758, \"end\": 1770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9466647183936499, \"rank\": 0.056337528773967395, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 1777, \"end\": 1782, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9998890600686198, \"rank\": 0.00011095172404725869, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], 