an intention\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2078}, {\"ngram\": \"any religious group\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2120}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'[The opening ceremony] tried to celebrate community tolerance.\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2197, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The opening ceremony\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2156}, {\"ngram\": \"community tolerance\", \"from\": 2177, \"to\": 2196}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We believe this ambition was achieved.\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2236, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this ambition\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If people have taken any offence we are really sorry.'\", \"from\": 2237, \"to\": 2291, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2246}, {\"ngram\": \"any offence\", \"from\": 2258, \"to\": 2269}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The opening ceremony's Artistic Director added: 'My wish is not to be subversive, nor to mock or to shock.\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2399, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The opening ceremony's Artistic Director\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2333}, {\"ngram\": \"My wish\", \"from\": 2342, \"to\": 2349}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Diversity means being together.\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2433, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Diversity\", \"from\": 2402, \"to\": 2411}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We wanted to include everyone, as simple as that.'\", \"from\": 2434, \"to\": 2484, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2463}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Criticism also came from further afield, with Germany's Bishop of Passau Stefan Oster saying: 'An impressive opening to hopefully peaceful games.\", \"from\": 2486, \"to\": 2631, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2532, \"end\": 2539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9972914541371345, \"rank\": 0.0026471916332184483, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q47602